# 💰 AI Personal Finance Behavior Analyzer

## 🚀 Overview
An AI-powered web app that analyzes user spending behavior, predicts future balance, detects anomalies, and provides actionable financial insights.

## 🔥 Features
- Expense categorization
- Anomaly detection (Isolation Forest)
- Balance forecasting (Prophet)
- Financial health score
- AI-based insights

## 🧠 Tech Stack
- Python, Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Prophet
- Streamlit

## 📊 Use Case
Helps users understand spending patterns and improve financial decisions.

## 🌐 Live Demo
https://personal-finance
-analyzer-gautam.streamlit.app

